import { Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import CardProduct from './Product'



const Products = () => {

  
  return (
    <>
    
     <Grid justify="center" spacing={3}>
       <Grid item xs={4} md={8} >
         <Typography>
           <CardProduct />
         </Typography>
       </Grid>
     </Grid>
    </>
  )
}

export default Products;
